values:
MAMAMAMA IS BACK. MAMA WET SELF FROM FEAR. 

MAMAMAMA USED BEAT MAMA WITH STICKS WITH NAILS IN THEM. MAMAMAMA USED ATTACK MY FACE WITH FISH WITH TEETH. MAMA BLEED SO MUCH. MAMA NOT WANT REMEMBER THINGS MAMA IS REMEMBERING. MAMA FEAR FOR BOY LIFE WHEN BOY WAS BORN. MAMA LOCK MAMAMAMA IN BASEMENT OF GINGERBREAD HOUSE WHERE MAMAMAMA MAKE MEAN EXPERIMENTS TURNING HUMAN LIFE INTO CANDIES THAT TASTE YUMMY.

MAMA SO SCARED THAT RAN AWAY FOREVER FROM DARK WOODS INTO KONOHA, MAMA THINK IS SAFE HERE. MAMA NOT REALIZE GINGERBREAD FALL APART AFTER 10 YEARS. MAMA SO SCARED. MAMA THINK WILL GET BEAT AGAIN. MAMA NOT KNOW WHAT TO DO. MAMA IS SO HORRIFIED.

MAMA HAVE URINE FALLING DOWN PANTS LEG FROM FEAR. 

MAMA SAY EVERYONE RUN WHILE CAN STILL RUN.

MAMA SAY IS NOT JOKE.

MAMA HAVE ONE THING TO SAY. MAMA READ BOY ENTRY ABOUT MAMA... BOY SAY THIS!

"My mom's a big liar"

MAMA CRY FOREVER... BUT MAMA NOT KNOW WHAT MEANT... MAMA HAD TRANSLATE. 

"MAMA TELL THINGS NOT REAL PLUS IS FAT" 

MAMA.... SAY BOY MAKE MAMA CRY OFTEN AT NIGHT. MAMA THINK MAN WITH GREEN AND SHINY TEETH NEED BE STOPPED.. MAMA SAY REVOLUTION!!! 

MAMA HAVE MEMORY... MAMA REMEMBER LONG TIME AGO... MAMA SEE BOY OUTSIDE PLAYING WITH DOG. MAMA WATCH DOG USE MOUTH TO BITE BOY IN LEG. MAMA LAUGH AT FIRST, BUT MAMA REALIZE MAMA NOT SUPPOSED TO LAUGH WHEN BOY BLEED SO MUCH FROM BODY. MAMA STILL FIND FUNNY, BUT MAMA GO OUTSIDE WITH BANDAID AND PUT ON BOY. MAMA ALSO THROW DOG INTO DITCH AND SET ON FIRE, BUT DOG OK. MAMA PUT WATER ON DOG AND NOW DOG IS GOOD AND LIVE WITH MAMA. BOY LOOK AT MAMA AND SAY "MAMA YOU IS BEST MAMA EVER" AND MAMA SO HAPPY THAT MAMA SMACK BOY SO HARD IN HIS FACE. MAMA NEVER BEEN HAPPIER EVER.

MAMA LOVE BOY. BOY NO LOVE MAMA. MAMA WONDER WHEN THIS ALL GOING TO END? MAMA MISS BOY MUCH. MAMA WISH BOY AND MAN NOT LIKE EACH OTHER. MAMA SAY MAN IS BAD. MAMA SAY EVERYONE IS NOT ABLE TO SEE BADNESS OF MAN. MAMA SEE BADNESS. MAMA SEE.

MAMA SAY IS TIME FOR CHANGE.

MAMA HAVE STORY SHARE WITH ALL PEOPLE WHO READ MAMA WORDS.

MAMA HAVE BOY, LONG TIME AGO. MAMA LOVE BOY, TRAIN BOY, SMACK BOY WITH LOVE, BEAT BOY ASS WITH JUSTICE... MAMA FEED BOY, MAMA HUG BOY, MAMA STAB BOY, MAMA SHOOT BOY... MAMA DO ALL THINGS MAMA SUPPOSED TO DO......

MAMA WATCH BOY GET OLD. MAMA WATCH BOY TAKE FIRST STEPS, MAMA WATCH BOY FALL ASLEEP, MAMA MAKE BOY SOUP WHEN HE'S SICK, MAMA POUR IT ON HIS HEAD. MAMA TAKE BOY TO SCHOOL, KISS HIM BYEBYE, MAMA DO EVERYTHING FOR BOY. MAMA KILL ANIMALS FOR BOY TO HAVE NEW CLOTHES. MAMA WATCH BOY GET FRIENDS. MAMA WATCH BOY CRY WHEN FRIEND SAY "BOY IS STUPID IN FACE" MAMA CONSOLE BY GROUNDING AND BEATING. MAMA DO THINGS RIGHT? MAMA WATCH WHEN NEW FRIENDS COME ALONG. 

MAMA SAD WHEN BOY GET NEW PET. MAMA ACCEPT THOUGH. MAMA OK WHEN SHE FIND OUT BOY IS RAPIST. MAMA EVEN LAUGH, MAMA WANT BETTER FOR HER BOY THOUGH. MAMA SAY IS BETTER NOW ABOUT THAT. MAMA SAY IS OK WHEN BOY IS GAY AND LIKE ASS. MAMA IS OK. MAMA ACCEPT ALL THINGS BOY DO...

MAMA SEE MAN TAKE BOY. MAMA NO LIKE MAN WHO WEAR GREEN WITH TEETH OF GLOWING. MAMA SAY IS NOT NATURAL. MAMA NO LIKE THAT MAN, FOREVER, NO LIKE THAT MAN. MAMA SAY IS BAD INFLUENCE. MAMA SAY MAN TOOK BOY WHO LOVE MAMA AND TURN HIM INTO BOY WHO NO LOVE MAMA EVER.... MAMA IS SAD.

MAMA BEEN THERE FOREVER, NOW MAMA CAST ASIDE LIKE GARBAGE... MAMA SAY NOT EVEN THE GOOD KIND YOU EAT WITH YOUR MOUTH. MAMA NO KNOW WHAT DO. MAMA IN ROOM WITH GLOWING THINGS, AND MAMA NO CAN ESCAPE OUT INTO WORLD. MAMA WONDER WHAT BOY DOING... 

MAMA WONDER WHY BOY LEFT MAMA SO ALONE...

MAMA CRY NOW. MAMA NO CAN TAKE THE BOY NO LOVING HER.

MAMA SAY GODDAMN MAMA HOTT NOWDAYS.

MAMA LOOK SO GOOD, PEOPLE ASK MAMA ALL TIME FOR SEX. MAMA SAY NO CAUSE MAMA NO WANT MAMA PARTS TO FALL OFF ON STREET WHERE PEOPLE CAN SAMPLE FOR FREE.

MAMA MILKSHAKE BRING ALL BOYS TO FENCED IN AREA... BUT REALLY IT NOT MILKSHAKE, MAMA MAKE OVALTINE.

BOY, MAMA SAY BETTER BE GOOD WHILE MAMA GONE, OR MAMA EAT SENSEI'S UNTIL SATISFIED....

MAMA GO BACK, MAMA HAVE AGENT TO MAKE HAPPY. MAMA GOOD. MAMA GOOD.

MAMA EDIT: MAMA SEND BOY LIGHTS OF BLACKNESS TO MAKE ROOM AND WHITE THINGS PURPLE. MAMA HOPE SHINY LIGHT KEEP BOY AWAY FROM DRUGS AND GAY PEOPLE.

MAMA FIND MAN CREEP IN BOY ROOM.

MAMA MAKE ALL SIN GO BYE BYE. MAMA MAKE MAN EAT SIN FOREVER. MAMA NO HAVE SIN WHERE LORD SEE FREELY!

MAMA NOW DO LAUNDRY. MAMA SAY MAN SMELL MUCH LIKE UNDERSIDES OF SICK DOG. MAMA JUST CLEAN SHEETS TOO.

MAMA SAY BOX WITH LETTER CONFUSE MAMA TO BURNING PLACE OF HOT.

MAMA ALSO SAY MAN IN COAT THAT SEXING MY BOY MAKE MAMA HAPPY IN LEG PLACES.

MAMA WISH TALK TO SOMEONE. MAMA NEVER TALK TO SOMEONE. MAMA SAD AND MAKE RAIN COME FROM LOOKING CIRCLES IN FACE.

MAMA GO NOW. MAMA COOK FISH. MAMA COOK BIG FISH. 

MAMA WANT FISH FOR ALL FRIENDS.
